# Legacy URL cleanup (SEO)
# old root blog routes -> language routes
/blog /en/blog/ 301
/blog/ /en/blog/ 301

# old markdown-like article URLs indexed by Google
/blog/:slug.md /en/blog/:slug/ 301
/blog/:slug.md/ /en/blog/:slug/ 301

# old root article paths -> English canonical
/blog/:slug /en/blog/:slug/ 301
/blog/:slug/ /en/blog/:slug/ 301
